    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_10_14585-14631",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "14585-14631",
      "markText": "扬州是江南顽强抵抗清军的第一座城，也可能满洲人想杀一儆百，于是下令屠城，破坏持续了十天以上。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=14585&rangeEnd=14631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=14585&rangeEnd=14631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_8_4140-4207",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4140-4207",
      "markText": "按照这样的逻辑推论下去，无疑可以一直追溯到人类起源，也就是追溯到人类受生之初所有胚胎都已蕴含死亡的基因。幸好我没有追步这类偏爱的愿望。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4140&rangeEnd=4207",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4140&rangeEnd=4207"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_4_2781-2853",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2781-2853",
      "markText": "多年来，我们的历史研究，过度热衷于所谓历史人物的评价，过度注目于某些历史积案的是非，而对于过程本身却往往不加细察，这难道不是非历史主义的态度吗？",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2781&rangeEnd=2853",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2781&rangeEnd=2853"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_12_5598-5622",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "5598-5622",
      "markText": "明朝文臣有一百余人丧生，而未战死的武将全部投降。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5598&rangeEnd=5622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5598&rangeEnd=5622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_8_1481-1566",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1481-1566",
      "markText": "严格地说，1644年并非明亡清兴的分界线。满洲领袖皇太极，还在1636年，就做了国号为清的新王朝皇帝了；而永历帝，明朝最后一名自称君临全中国的亲王，却到1662年才被灭。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1481&rangeEnd=1566",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1481&rangeEnd=1566"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_4_557-619",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "557-619",
      "markText": "历史也真古怪。有时上百年过去了，留下的记录平淡无奇。但有那么若干瞬间反而在后世会激起回响，并且引发历史学家们不倦的探索兴味。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=619",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=619"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_11_21286-21315",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "21286-21315",
      "markText": "这就是博洛军离杭州只有十天路程之时黄道周所提出的各项要务！",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21286&rangeEnd=21315",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21286&rangeEnd=21315"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_8_9409-9597",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9409-9597",
      "markText": "在一次“轻举妄动”中，被他的首席太监诱出举行有勇无谋亲征的皇帝，做了西蒙古酋长的俘虏并被扣留年余，从而在明廷引发了一场巨大危机。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9409&rangeEnd=9597",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9409&rangeEnd=9597"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_4_1136-1220",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1136-1220",
      "markText": "待到18世纪后期乾隆皇帝出于实用的考虑，将当年曾为清朝统一全国立下大功的故明降官降将贬作“贰臣”，意外地造成南明史研究变相开禁，那时有关南明的历史陈述早已残缺混乱不堪。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1136&rangeEnd=1220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1136&rangeEnd=1220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_8_17223-17262",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "17223-17262",
      "markText": "这个首辅位置连对最柔顺谦和的在职者都是座烤炉，而且得随时充当皇帝过失的替罪羊。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17223&rangeEnd=17262",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17223&rangeEnd=17262"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_5_2171-2223",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2171-2223",
      "markText": "在统一的文官国家制度发育较早的中国，汉民族为主体的民族主义意识早已形成，它的存在并不借助现代国家的形成。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2171&rangeEnd=2223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2171&rangeEnd=2223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_8_11808-11881",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11808-11881",
      "markText": "诉诸武力等于承认文治的失败”，他们“高瞻远瞩地主张，尽可能不用暴力以维持秩序”；即使战争不可避免，他们仍然认为，“战争过于复杂，不能让武人擅自处理",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11808&rangeEnd=11881",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11808&rangeEnd=11881"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_9_12880-12936",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12880-12936",
      "markText": "可从中央政府获得钱粮供给，每卒每年银二十两。各镇若收复失地，即受其管辖；不论何人，若收复一块地方，即任为该地长官",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019446&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12880&rangeEnd=12936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf632610716e81f6cf60a13?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12880&rangeEnd=12936"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019446_10_21342-21427",
